	   <tr><td colspan=2>Would have to disagree as i have lvled 3 toons to 9 in misty then headed to commons to solo cats and bears to 11 and 12.&nbsp;&nbsp; In misty stay away from guards yes but that is a given.  go for the 3 goblin camps and remember to zone into runnyeye in case of problems.  there are bears for good exp here too.  I ran a human mage, a half elf bard, and halfling cleric to 9 here.<br>  I have run 3 toons though the crushbone area also but from 10 to 12 there is gap in cons of cent to lego that i would leave the area gain some lvls and come back at 12 to 13. at 12 I would hit everfrost and use Bellow lvl12 and selo to kite mammoth and cats.  its Slow but easy to solo.  groups are better and closer to most areas   <br>&nbsp;<br>Servant to Veeshen on Povar</td></tr>
